{
  "stem": "18061.3",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 161.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we had to put together cotton with cotton, silks with silk, and-- and the same thing with shoes.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That's-- most of us, we worked over there, besides some people that worked in the kitchen, or some people who-- that worked in other places.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But too many people never was in the workings commando from Treblinka.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The top number reached up to 800 was allowed.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, there's not too much to tell about, because those people were already undressed and going into the gas chamber, which [INAUDIBLE], nobody could go, because nobody ever returned that road.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "What I found out is, when I was assigned as a barber to cut the woman's hair in the gas chamber-- that was the beginning, then we did cut women's hair in the gas chamber-- then, I find out what it is and how it was.",
      "word_count": 46
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, from both side, from both side enclose-- not only what it was enclosed, it wasn't enclosed by buildings, but trees from both sides, which nobody could escape from this side, though.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was no place where it was escaped.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And beside that, there were the Germans.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And there were-- there were the Ukrainians holding their post around.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So people, they could not-- they had to go in, direct to the gas chamber.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The physical layout of the gas chambers.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was entirely a different-- not only barrack, different place.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Nobody but nobody could go near from the place-- they call this the larger-- one to number two, because the number two was actually the death lager.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That's what they called it, because, over there, the job is only by killing people.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Whoever went over there from the lager number one could never return back to lager number one.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
